<h1>声</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">shēng</span><span class=alesi>(sheng1)</span> , sheng , <span style="color:#000099;">qìng</span><span class=alesi>(qing4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 声 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 声</h2><div class=abo>
